   Grp; IEEE Cloud Comp; Business Proc Integrat \& Management; IT Profess;
   Intl Journal Web Serv Res; Comp Now Access Discover Engage; IEEE
   Transact Serv Comp},
Abstract = {Industrial processes provide lots of operational data on different
   timescales. Those data are well-structured and used now for daily
   control, longer-term management and forensics. We propose to pre-process
   that data and treat them the way the natural language processing is
   done-first, in order to find common ways the process is controlled. Such
   knowledge can then be used in prediction or early detection of faults,
   or necessary manufacturing shifts. Gas transmission operational data are
   considered here as the live example.},
